{"type":"answer","id":28701,"parentType":"question","parentId":6978,"uid":4516,"contents":"权威发布，就是点回车键的<b>权</b>力在<b>维</b>尼的<b>发布。</b><br>\n<br>\n发布的东西可以是下面人编写的，但是「微博发布」键必须由维尼锤下去。所谓“一锤定音”，所谓“党媒姓党，定于一尊”。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qRxB6Uv.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qRxB6Uv.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qRxB6Uv.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-01-18","agreeCount":9,"discussionCount":0}